{"tid":1332220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚］所有勇武入嚟傾下721夢遊邊度","createTime":"2019-07-19T08:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T14:45:43.000Z","uid":54813,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"888ab710110be7fd0405f48ae4c441fa3117c211","tid":1332220,"uid":54813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:35:23.000Z","msg":"721仲未有決定去邊度夢遊<br />\n無無謂謂搵個地方又冇乜意義<br />\n以下有幾個地點都同反送中好有關<br />\n到時散場遍地開花<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 沙頭角邊境</span></span></strong><br />\n深圳同香港之間有道隨意門<br />\n大陸人可以唔經關口直入香港境內<br />\n一定要關注下佢！<br />\n<br />\n【推上熱門】痴撚線點解無人知呢單野！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327671</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 屯門深圳灣大橋</span></span></strong><br />\n深圳灣大橋係搞到屯門淪陷嘅主因之一<br />\n嚟緊明日大嶼規劃都同深圳灣大橋環環相扣<br />\n一定要關注下佢！<br />\n<br />\n有圖 (港珠澳/人工島/明日大嶼/屯赤連接路/深圳灣大橋)陰謀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308864</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 赤鱲角機場</span></span></strong><br />\n港豬澳同三跑兩個大白象都喺哂呢度<br />\n而且香港國際機場有咩事全世界新聞都一定會報導<br />\n<br />\n郭文貴：將會進行二次佔中，佔領機場後直接癱瘓香港，林鄭就會下台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1209992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1209992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 蒲台島</span></strong></span><br />\n大家唔好笑我係真心嘅<br />\n島上面地勢平坦而且係少有冇警崗嘅大面積島嶼<br />\n作為香港南極係香港距離中國大陸最遙遠嘅地方<br />\n如果有滋事份子佔島成立臨時政權政府中共都幾難阻止同清場<br />\n<br />\n［理性分析］香港成立臨時政權一定會係全世界頭條<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331753\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331753</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d45c59549fb685b8c61272ea53132401857a157","tid":1332220,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:40:02.000Z","msg":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"f07861c06edf7209c4554467dbd6454d6e39105a","tid":1332220,"uid":62674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"禮賓府呢？"},{"pid":"3060b13561f05dab1306f50fbedde00ae3042fc2","tid":1332220,"uid":54813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f07861c06edf7209c4554467dbd6454d6e39105a","tid":1332220,"uid":62674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T09:06:00.000Z","msg":"禮賓府呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"行斜路不了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}